Of course, every project is challenging but this one a bit special, Here's why!

It involves a total of 7 components/services. 1 out of 7 components is actually built ground up. The rest of the components already exists eg., Kubernetes, Docker, Airflow. It's the matter of bringing them all together.

Sounds easy right?

Now I look at it, yes it is not so hard.

But two weeks back I had very little clue what the 6 components did, whether they had the necessary functionality. It took me 2 weeks to understand if the 6 components match the requirement we are looking for.
